    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The study of the history of book production and the description of books as physical objects, including study of the relationships of varying texts or multiple editions of a work.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
